      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it's a bit high-level. could you dig deeper into the economic and social side of it? like, what are the core arguments regarding the impact on domestic labor markets or social services? i really want them to have those specific, heavy-hitting points so they aren't caught off guard by a really well-prepared opponent.",
